{
  "stem": "22840.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was just where no-- no-- no forest there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was-- it was not a-- it was a natural forest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was not a made forest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was a very big tree at the edge of the clearing, at the corner of the clearing, peculiar looking tree, outstanding from the other trees.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we-- we ran toward the tree.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were-- she was killed next to the tree with my sister in the clearing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Maybe if we could get into the woods, she would not be killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Everything is split second.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was wounded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was-- I was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I was standing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I was-- I was-- I was crying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Before that, I remember we were not walking on the-- on the-- we were walking on the side of the road, the side of this flows, this little river, the flow.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There was a bridge, a stone bridge, not wooden bridge, not metal, stone-- stone bridge [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] on-- above this little flow.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So I remember that place there where it happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Apparently, he took me up the mountains with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't know I was wounded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was wounded in my left leg above the knee.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was wearing what-- what we may call today woolen tights.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Children wear them-- wore them, very high woolen socks, with things which, kind of garters which keep them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Boys, girls-- boys didn't walk with long pants, only adults.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Children had short pants even-- even in winter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we had these woolen thick socks.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
